<br>
Camps may or may not be respected.  A lot of it is going to depend on who is doing the camping and who is looking to gank the camper.  No one should operate under the illusion that the old Sol B system still applies.  If you don't have a killing force in Skyfire when Ragefire pops, you're at risk of getting ganked.<br>
<br>
In response to your comment, Hoppkins, I hope that people will be smart enough not to camp the spawn for six days.  There are many of us who are either unable or unwilling to camp a spawn for six days, but we still intend to get our epics at some point.  Given that reality, a cleric isn't likely to get a lot of respect by sitting in a safe spot in Skyfire for six days and hitting a &quot;Ragefire is camped&quot; hotkey.  That takes us back to where this whole discussion started several weeks ago. <p>Sagemon Prayeth<BR>
High Priest of Quellious the Tranquil<BR>A Twist of Fate</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/uglorianafrostglitter.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Gloriana Frostglitter</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Veteran</span><br>  Posts: 1387<br> <font color=#E9D756>(4/18/02 9:38:07 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/femarrgeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=9342.topic&index=71>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Ragefire Meeting 5/6 - Report</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr>  a cleric isn't likely to get a lot of respect by sitting in a safe spot in Skyfire for six days and hitting a &quot;Ragefire is camped&quot; hotkey.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
<br>
Sagemon, please amend that to read: &quot;A cleric isn't likely to get a lot of respect by sitting in a safe spot in Skyfire for six days and hitting a &quot;Ragefire is camped&quot; hotkey from <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>  me</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->&quot;. Hopefully, your selfish attitude is not typical of the majority of this server.<br>
<br>
Verant screwed the Ragefire spawn, it completely sucks and is unfair to clerics in so many ways.  That being said, if anyone has the stones to sit there for 6 days, they have my respect and my assistance killing Ragefire if I'm around and they need it.  A camping cleric is making all kinds of sacrifices (specifically real life sacrifices) and the thought that they would sit there for 6 days and some other group would not allow them the chance to mobilize (30-45 minutes or so) when he finally spawns, is very very disturbing.<br>
<br>
